This marketing site includes:

✅ Complete Vite + React + Tailwind setup
✅ Dark theme with #9D00FF primary color
✅ Orbitron + Nunito Sans fonts
✅ Auto-playing hero video & background audio
✅ Parallax effects with framer-motion
✅ 72-hour offer timer with localStorage
✅ Functional chat widget
✅ Contact form with backend integration
✅ Responsive design for all devices
✅ SEO optimized with meta tags
✅ PWA ready with manifest

To run:

Bash

cd marketing
npm install
npm run dev
The site will connect to your existing backend API for chat, contact forms, and user authentication. All the Egyptian mystique + futuristic intelligence aesthetic is implemented with proper animations and interactions.